comments: Holmes (SAC) swipes down and makes contact with Doncic's (DAL) elbow during his driving shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) briefly engages with Barea (DAL) along the perimeter, but does not affect his ability to defend the pass.
Barea (DAL) swings up and makes contact with the under side of Barnes' (SAC) left arm after his gather, affecting his driving shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) makes contact with Finney-Smith's (DAL) left arm/shoulder during rebounding, but it is marginal and does not affect Finney-Smith's ability to retrieve the ball.
Porzingis (DAL) makes incidental body contact with Holmes (SAC) as they each attempt to retrieve the rebound.
Doncic (DAL) makes marginal contact with his left hand to Joseph's (SAC) front prior to his step-back and doesn't affect Joseph's ability to defend.
Joseph (SAC) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Doncic (DAL) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) makes clean contact with the ball before making incidental contact with Porzingis' (DAL) left hand during rebounding.
Bogdanovic (SAC) engages with Finney-Smith (DAL) after the release of the jump shot attempt and makes some contact with his side, but it is marginal.
Hield (SAC) establishes position in the front court within eight seconds.

Hield (SAC) makes some contact with his off-arm to Barea's (DAL) face/shoulder, but it is marginal. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Barea (DAL) makes marginal body contact with Barnes (SAC) in the post.
Barea (DAL) makes marginal contact as he contests Barnes' (SAC) turn-around shot attempt in the post.
Porzingis (DAL) makes marginal contact without extending his off-arm to Holmes' (SAC) front at the start and end of the drive.
Holmes (SAC) clamps Porzingis' (DAL) right arm and grabs his jersey, affecting his ability to rebound.
Doncic (DAL) briefly has his arm around Barnes' (SAC) upper-half and slides it off in a continuous motion.
Barnes (SAC) makes marginal contact with his left hand forearm to Doncic's (DAL) front as the pass is made.
Barnes (SAC) gathers the ball and proceeds to take two legal steps prior to his release of his shot attempt.
Porzingis (DAL) makes marginal contact with Barnes' (SAC) front during the driving shot attempt.
Joseph (SAC) makes contact with Doncic's (DAL) right elbow during his upward motion and affects his driving shot attempt.
SAC is awarded the timeout prior to any deemed illegal contact made by Barea (DAL) to Holmes (SAC).
Bjelica (SAC) makes marginal contact with Finney-Smith's (DAL) backside as the screen is set.
